# Compile from source

## Mac user? You might want to install GSL first: 'brew install gsl'

## Download the zip file.
wget https://github.com/sinarueeger/ssimp_software/archive/master.zip

## Unpack the zip file with 
unzip master.zip

## access the folder
cd ssimp_software-master

## run the makefile (source compilation)
make

## Download required build database
bin/ssimp --download.build.db

## run your first summary statistics imputation on a test file
bin/ssimp --gwas gwas/small.random.txt --ref ref/small.vcf.sample.vcf.gz --out output.txt

## Do you have a *reference panel* stored somewhere? 

    ## YES: Good!
        Is it 1000genomes?
        ## YES: go to line 93 in https://github.com/sinarueeger/ssimp_software/blob/master/doc/usage.txt
        ## NO: go to line 114 in https://github.com/sinarueeger/ssimp_software/blob/master/doc/usage.txt

